gameObjects

Class GameObjectXT

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.gameengine.icadroids.objects.GameObject
      • gameObjects.GameObjectXT
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Block, MoveableGameObject

    public class GameObjectXT
extends GameObject
    Extension on GameObject. Important! Call GameObjectXT.setBoundingBox AFTER dimensions and location for this GameObjectXT are defined or boundingBox for this GameObjectXT will not function properly. (Game engine limitation)
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.0 $
    Author:
    Tim Wostemeier
